question: How do I confirm my pre-registration request is completed?
text:
How do I confirm my pre-registration request is completed? 
          
        
An automated system that can update your pre-registration status has yet to be developed. If you successfully pre-registered by the September 2
nd
 deadline, you should have received information on how to access the Pennie training information on September 16. If you have pre-registered and have not yet received information on how to complete training, please contact Pennie at 1-844-844-8040.
